name: The super alliance civilization is heading to the 2D universe. Did you get the ticket? ╭(°A°`)╮
description: To escape from the unstoppable fall from the 3D universe to 2D, the super civilizations have already modified themselves become 2D creature and migrated to the 2D universe. However, we have not got our tickets yet, only waiting to be swamped by the raging vortex of time and space behind us.
